Ms. Pascal?

924
01:02:21,904 --> 01:02:24,634
- Ms. Pascal?
- Mr. Crick.

925
01:02:25,341 --> 01:02:27,832
- Hi.
- Hi.

926
01:02:28,277 --> 01:02:30,837
- Hi.
- Hi.

927
01:02:31,047 --> 01:02:33,015
I'm glad I caught you.

928
01:02:33,850 --> 01:02:35,147
Oh, yeah? Why?

929
01:02:36,452 --> 01:02:39,819
Because I wanted
to bring these to you.

930
01:02:41,591 --> 01:02:43,786
- Really?
- Yeah.

931
01:02:43,993 --> 01:02:48,362
So you can't accept gifts,
but you can give them?

932
01:02:49,298 --> 01:02:50,390
- Listen...
- I don't know.

933
01:02:50,600 --> 01:02:53,034
That seems a little inconsistent,
doesn't it, Mr. Crick?

934
01:02:53,236 --> 01:02:54,464
Very inconsistent, yes.

935
01:02:54,670 --> 01:02:57,002
I'll tell you what.
I'll purchase them.

936
01:02:57,206 --> 01:02:58,673
- No.
- No, no, no, really...

937
01:02:58,875 --> 01:03:01,241
...I'd like to purchase them.
What are they?

938
01:03:02,211 --> 01:03:03,610
Flours.

939
01:03:04,280 --> 01:03:07,716
- What?
- I brought you flours.

940
01:03:18,594 --> 01:03:22,587
And you carried them
all the way here?

941
01:03:24,233 --> 01:03:29,364
Ms. Pascal, I've been odd
and I know that I've been odd.

942
01:03:30,406 --> 01:03:33,204
And I want you.

943
01:03:33,743 --> 01:03:36,211
- What?
- There's so many reasons.

944
01:03:36,412 --> 01:03:39,575
There's so many influences in my life
that are telling me...

945
01:03:39,782 --> 01:03:41,340
...at times quite literally...

946
01:03:41,551 --> 01:03:44,349
...that I should come here
and bring you these...

947
01:03:45,421 --> 01:03:47,719
...but I'm doing this
because I want you.

948
01:03:48,825 --> 01:03:50,690
You want me?

949
01:03:51,194 --> 01:03:53,719
In no uncertain terms.

950
01:03:56,532 --> 01:04:01,765
Isn't there some very clear
and established...

951
01:04:01,971 --> 01:04:05,600
...rule about fraternization?

952
01:04:05,808 --> 01:04:08,003
- Auditor-auditee protocol?
- Yeah.

953
01:04:08,211 --> 01:04:10,475
Yeah, but I don't care.

954
01:04:11,047 --> 01:04:14,210
- Why?
- Because I want you.

955
01:04:19,755 --> 01:04:20,722
Well...

956
01:04:22,992 --> 01:04:25,893
...do you mind carrying those
a little bit further?

957
01:04:26,729 --> 01:04:28,060
Okay.

958
01:04:30,833 --> 01:04:32,232
Okay.

959
01:04:46,082 --> 01:04:47,879
Did you make a key?

960
01:04:48,084 --> 01:04:50,245
No, I just committed it to memory.

961
01:04:50,453 --> 01:04:54,514
- The blue, that's barley flour.
- What's that one?

962
01:04:54,724 --> 01:04:56,089
- The orange?
- Yeah.

963
01:04:56,292 --> 01:04:57,884
I forget.

964
01:04:58,494 --> 01:04:59,461
Right here.

965
01:05:03,099 --> 01:05:04,794
Do you wanna come up?

966
01:05:07,270 --> 01:05:09,795
