whose prior work...

1016
01:10:41,237 --> 01:10:43,933
...would seem to make them
candidates to write your story...

1017
01:10:44,139 --> 01:10:46,835
...based on the criteria you and I
previously determined.

1018
01:10:47,042 --> 01:10:51,240
If your narrator is alive,
she's on this list.

1019
01:10:51,981 --> 01:10:54,882
But it appears the list
is of little use to you now.

1020
01:10:55,084 --> 01:10:57,052
Now that you're gonna live
happily ever after.

1021
01:10:57,253 --> 01:11:01,815
Oh, goodie. This woman, Karen Eiffel,
she's one of my favorite authors.

1022
01:11:02,024 --> 01:11:03,355
<i>- Hi.</i>
<i>- Hi.</i>

1023
01:11:03,559 --> 01:11:05,652
