My daughter's name is Mrs. Epstein.

1138
01:18:48,890 --> 01:18:51,256
<i>The first phone</i>
<i>failed to give a dial tone.</i>

1139
01:18:52,360 --> 01:18:54,157
<i>And the second</i>
<i>seemed to be splattered...</i>

1140
01:18:54,362 --> 01:18:56,159
<i>... with a fresh batch of mucus.</i>

1141
01:18:58,567 --> 01:19:00,626
<i>Harold dialed the third phone...</i>

1142
01:19:00,836 --> 01:19:05,500
<i>... fervently making sure to give each</i>
<i>number key a specific forceful push.</i>

1143
01:19:27,062 --> 01:19:28,495
Don't answer that!

1144
01:19:28,697 --> 01:19:30,597
Didn't you say this phone never r...?

1145
01:19:58,727 --> 01:20:01,025
- Hello?
- Is this Karen Eiffel?

1146
01:20:01,229 --> 01:20:02,890
- Yes.
- My name is Harold Crick.

1147
01:20:03,098 --> 01:20:05,259
I believe you're writing a story
about me.

1148
01:20:06,268 --> 01:20:10,068
- I'm sorry?
- My name is Harold Crick.

1149
01:20:10,772 --> 01:20:13,263
- Is this a joke?
